            </div>
            <div id="board-grid" class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-1.5 md:gap-2 aspect-[6/5] max-h-[340px] md:max-h-[380px] w-full mx-auto"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 items-stretch h-[160px] md:h-[180px]">
            <div class="glass rounded-3xl p-2 flex flex-col justify-between items-center text-center bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 to-transparent relative">
                <div class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold tracking-tight">주사위 컨트롤</div>
                <div class="scene" id="dice-trigger" onclick="rollDice3D()">
                    <div class="cube show-5" id="dice-cube">
                        <div class="cube__face cube__face--1">●</div>
                        <div class="cube__face cube__face--2">··</div>
                        <div class="cube__face cube__face--3">···</div>
                        <div class="cube__face cube__face--4 text-red-600">∷</div>
                        <div class="cube__face cube__face--5">⁙</div>
                        <div class="cube__face cube__face--6">⁛</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button id="btn-roll" onclick="rollDice3D()" class="w-full py-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-500 text-black font-black text-xs rounded-xl shadow-md active:scale-95 transition-all">
                    터치해서 굴리기
                </button>
            </div>

            <div id="question-panel" class="col-span-2 glass rounded-3xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between border border-white/10 transition-colors duration-300">
                <div id="panel-header" class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-white/5 pb-1">
                    <span id="panel-badge" class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black bg-white/10 text-gray-400 uppercase">대기 중</span>
                    <span id="panel-q-num" class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-bold font-mono">SPACE #00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="my-auto py-1">
                    <h3 id="panel-title" class="text-sm md:text-lg font-black break-keep leading-snug text-gray-400 text-center">
                        주사위를 굴리거나 말판을 눌러 대화를 나누세요!
                    </h3>
                    <p id="panel-desc" class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 text-center break-keep leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        총 100개의 소그룹 전용 질문이 랜덤하게 매칭됩니다.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div id="dice-result-guide" class="text-center text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-medium">
                    대화 후 주사위를 다음 사람에게 넘겨주세요.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="w-full text-center py-2 text-[10px] text-gray-600 font-medium">
        © 2026 Church Group Board Game Project. 100 Questions Ready.
    </footer>

